title: Angels win 2-1 to prevent Rangers from clinching AL West
text:
> Texas Angels win 2-1 to prevent Rangers from clinching AL West Texas Rangers Delino DeShields, bottom slides under third base against Los Angeles Angels third baseman David Freese (6) after DeShields was tagged out trying to steal during the first inning of a baseball game in Arlington, Texas, Friday, Oct. 2, 2015.
